Title: Bosonization of quantum sine-Gordon field with a boundary
Authors: Bo-yu Hou, Kang-jie Shi, Yan-shen Wang and Wen-li Yang
Comments: Latex 25pages
Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A12 (1997) 1711-1741
\\
  Boundary operators and boundary ground states in sine-Gordon model with a
fixed boundary condition are studied using bosonization and q-deformed
oscillators.We also obtain the form-factors of this model.
